targets.query:
day = from(bucket: "HomeEnergy")
  |> range(start: -7d, stop: now())
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "P1")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["unit"] == "kWh")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "ELECTRICITY_USED_TARIFF_2")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1h, fn: spread, createEmpty: false)
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 24h, fn: sum, createEmpty: false)
  |> set(key: "_field", value:"Day")

night = from(bucket: "HomeEnergy")
  |> range(start: -7d, stop: now())
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "P1")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["unit"] == "kWh")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "ELECTRICITY_USED_TARIFF_1")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1h, fn: spread, createEmpty: false)
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 24h, fn: sum, createEmpty: false)
  |> set(key: "_field", value:"Night")
  
  //|> rename(columns: {"ELECTRICITY_USED_TARIFF_1": "Nacht", "ELECTRICITY_USED_TARIFF_2": "Dag"})
union(tables: [day, night])
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value", "_field"])

from(bucket: "HomeEnergy")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: now())
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "P1")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["unit"] == "kW")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "CURRENT_ELECTRICITY_USAGE")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1h, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 24h, fn: sum, createEmpty: false)
  |> set(key: "_field", value:"Day + Night")
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value", "_field"])
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "HomeNibe")

  |> yield(name: "mean")

day = from(bucket: "HomeEnergy")
